.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: radish, grapefruit, nectarine, spinach
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, collecting, puzzles, baking
4 different pets are kept: snake, fish, pony, bird
1. the person eating grapefruit is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
3. the owner of the snake is the person eating grapefruit##1
4. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1
6. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
7. the person eating spinach is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | nectarine   | spinach      | grapefruit       | radish |
| Hobby   | skydiving | baking | puzzles     | collecting |
| Pet     | bird     | fish  | snake | pony |

