.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, water, coffee
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, musical, adventure, western
4 different pets are kept: dog, bird, turtle, frog
1. the owner of the turtle is the person watching epic movies##1
2. the owner of the bird is between the person watching western movies and the owner of the dog##2
3. the person watching western movies is the person drinking milk##1
4. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
5. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4
6. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person watching epic movies is the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the owner of the turtle is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | water   | coffee          | milk | iced-tea        |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure     | musical | western   | epic     |
| Pet           | dog | bird         | frog         | turtle |

