.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, board-games, reading, card-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, photographer, mechanic, nurse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, d&b, metal, r&b
1. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
2. the mechanic is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the nurse is the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the fan of metal##1
5. the fan of d&b is between the security-guard and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
6. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is reading##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | board-games | magic-tricks      | reading       | card-games    |
| Job           | photographer  | mechanic  | nurse | security-guard |
| Music-Genre   | r&b      | metal | d&b         | punk    |

