.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, almond-milk, juice
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, dressmaker, lawyer, librarian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, juice-polo, soccer, golf
1. the project-manager is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the project-manager##3
3. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the project-manager##3
4. the person who's sport is juice-polo is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
6. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the project-manager##1
7. the project-manager is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
8. the dressmaker is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
9. the librarian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | mirinda         | 7up  | almond-milk     | juice         |
| Job        | librarian | dressmaker | project-manager | lawyer         |
| Sport      | juice-polo         | soccer  | climbing   | golf |

