.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, house, rock, d&b
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, colombian, british, french
4 different pets are kept: ferret, cat, goldfish, hamster
 1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
 2. the thai is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the cat is on the right of the fan of house##1
 4. the british is between the fan of house and the fan of trance##2
 5. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
 6. the owner of the hamster is the fan of rock##1
 7. the french is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of trance is in an odd position##4
 9. the colombian is between the fan of d&b and the fan of rock##2
10. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | rock    | house | d&b    |
| Nationality   | thai | british | colombian  | french |
| Pet           | goldfish   | hamster    | ferret        | cat   |

