.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, lemonade, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, writer, accountant, dancer
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, german, american, turkish
1. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3
2. the writer is on the left of the mechanic##1
3. the turkish is on the left or right of the accountant##3
4. the writer is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the mechanic##1
6. the turkish is on the right of the writer##1
7. the german is on the left of the writer##1
8. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the german##3
9. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | fanta                | water  | hot-chocolate | lemonade   |
| Job           | dancer | writer | mechanic   | accountant |
| Nationality   | german         | chinese     | turkish     | american |

