.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: papaya, mango, cauliflower, kale
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, time-travel, documentary, zombie
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, disco, indie, salsa
1. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating kale##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is on the far left##1
3. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
4. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the fan of gospel is between the person watching zombie movies and the fan of salsa##2
6. the person watching documentary movies is in an even position##4
7. the person eating papaya is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | cauliflower    | mango  | kale  | papaya |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | time-travel | martial-arts | documentary |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | gospel     | salsa    | disco |

