.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, iced-tea, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, british, french, nigerian
4 different pets are kept: fish, lizard, bird, dog
1. the owner of the lizard is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the italian##2
2. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
3. the french is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
4. the owner of the dog is on the left of the british##1
5. the owner of the dog is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
7. the italian is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
8. the french is the person drinking tea##1
9. the nigerian is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | tea | hot-chocolate      | iced-tea  | soy-milk    |
| Nationality   | french   | british | nigerian | italian |
| Pet           | dog      | bird       | lizard   | fish      |

