.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, puzzles, collecting, baking
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, egyptian, german, argentine
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, swimming, rowing, tennis
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's sport is sailing##2
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is baking is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
6. the argentine is between the person who's sport is sailing and the brazilian##2
7. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1
8. the egyptian is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is sailing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | fishing    | collecting | puzzles  | baking  |
| Nationality   | german | egyptian       | argentine | brazilian |
| Sport         | rowing   | sailing      | tennis | swimming       |

