.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, volleyball, soccer, rugby
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, helicopter, jet-ski, train
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
5. the person drinking coffee is between the person driving the helicopter and the person who's sport is soccer##2
6. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who's sport is rugby##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate    | coffee     | iced-tea    | soy-milk        |
| Sport       | soccer   | skateboarding | volleyball | rugby |
| Transport   | train | jet-ski      | helicopter    | quad-bike   |

