.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-17::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, asparagus, potato, kiwi
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, zombie, crime, western
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, dutch, spanish, thai
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
2. the malaysian is between the dutch and the person eating kiwi##2
3. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
4. the person eating asparagus is on the far left or far right##3
5. the malaysian is on the left of the dutch##1
6. the person eating asparagus is in an odd position##4
7. the spanish is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating kiwi is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | asparagus | kiwi  | watermelon   | potato    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports  | crime     | western | zombie |
| Nationality   | spanish   | thai | malaysian | dutch   |

