.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-18::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, baking, rock-climbing, drawing
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, analyst, electrician, architect
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, american, polish, pakistani
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an odd position##4
2. the electrician is on the right of the polish##1
3. the scientist is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the analyst##1
5. the polish is on the right of the nigerian##1
6. the scientist is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the electrician##1
8. the american is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |        4        |
| Hobby         | drawing | rock-climbing   | photography    | baking    |
| Job           | architect   | analyst    | scientist | electrician |
| Nationality   | american    | nigerian | polish    | pakistani         |

