.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, cherry, grapes, plum
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, photography, rock-climbing, video-games
4 different pets are kept: lizard, snake, goat, ferret
1. the person eating grapefruit is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
4. the person eating grapes is on the far left##1
5. the person eating cherry is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
7. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
8. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | grapes    | cherry    | grapefruit  | plum |
| Hobby   | video-games | photography | cooking | rock-climbing      |
| Pet     | snake   | lizard        | ferret   | goat       |

 